title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Megabucks' game
maintext:
MADISON, Wis. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Wisconsin Lottery’s “Megabucks” game were:
06-09-19-30-40-42
(six, nine, nineteen, thirty, forty, forty-two)
